snippet.title: 3D Kaleidoscope: Baby Universe - PS1 (1997)
snippet.description: Obscure JPN PS1 game. The visuals are really amazing. You can also swap the game out for a music CD while it's running and make effects that way. I grabbed the two nearest CDs to try with it, Dreamrunner - Clouds from the East, and Jan Hammer - Beyond the Mind's Eye, credits to those great artists.
